{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"5140c33r92iek34sfwgie7u","title":"OSCP","desc":"","updated":1691143402585,"created":1691075570149,"custom":{},"fname":"Security.OSCP","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"b77af6a59c238ce679766477c2515ad8","links":[],"anchors":{"kali-linux-渗透测试-一般课程信息":{"type":"header","text":"Kali Linux 渗透测试 一般课程信息","value":"kali-linux-渗透测试-一般课程信息","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["isvlzihchfp0tsqlfi5f97c","594yeuwf7d0gn28td1z29dz","77tp3ycq0578u3kuitpy1vo"],"parent":"fzxc4lax935ogwcc4t5gzb8","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"oscp\">OSCP<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#oscp\"></a></h1>\n<p>OSCP 是一个渗透测试认证，这个认证必须经过 PWK（Kali Linux 渗透测试 一般课程）课程的学习后才能考。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"kali-linux-渗透测试-一般课程信息\">Kali Linux 渗透测试 一般课程信息<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kali-linux-渗透测试-一般课程信息\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>PWK课程组成</strong> \n<ul>\n<li><strong>PWK 课程材料</strong> ： 以邮件的方式下发 PDF 文档、视频课程</li>\n<li><strong>访问实验室网络的VPN ：</strong>当课程开始时，VPN凭据和连接包一同以邮件方式下发</li>\n<li><strong>学生论坛证书</strong>：  学生论坛不要发布完整的解决方案，考试通过将获得证书持有人的访问权限。</li>\n<li><strong>现场支持</strong>： 可以与学生管理员沟通，寻求帮助。</li>\n<li><strong>OSCP 尝试考试</strong>： 初次购买PWK课程,在实验室时间结束后120天时间过期，如果考试过期或未通过，可以购买考试延期。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>获取帮助</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.offensiver-security.com/\">https://support.offensiver-security.com/</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.offensiver-security.com/faq\">https://www.offensiver-security.com/faq</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/isvlzihchfp0tsqlfi5f97c\">Windows命令</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/594yeuwf7d0gn28td1z29dz\">linux命令</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/77tp3ycq0578u3kuitpy1vo\">方法论</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"","updated":1691107996619,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"nam